<br>
Ghitming<br>
<br>
I was building my monk's 2hb skill, and asked if it would be ok to practice on  some of Ghitming's (and his group's) pulls while in KC. He didn't hesitate to  let me. He then apologized that there was not enough room to invite me into  the group (despite the fact my 2hb was pathetic, ergo, so was my damage). <br>
When the group left, he attempted to give me a Drolvarg mantle.<br>
<br>
A few days later while I was in SolB he gave me a /tell letting me know that  he had just killed the Guano Harvester and that I was free to loot the Large   Soiled Bag (the bags are treasured by monks).<br>
<br>
There always seems to be a shortage of pulls in SolB, and Ghitming has      repeatedly allowed me to pull *his* mobs.<br>
<br>
He is an asset to your guild guild, and I'm sure he is a wonderful officer. <br>
<br>
                  Thank you.<br>
<br>
                  Sincerely,<br>
<br>
                  Knomraski, Iksar Disciple of the 54th fist <br>
